  abilityName: Star Fall
  description: "You never suffer Damage from falling, unless\nlanding on something
    harmful. When you\nland from a fall of at least 12ft you may\nrelease a shockwave
    (d8 blast).\nPASSION - Authenticity\nRestore SPI when you reveal your identity
    or\nintentions at an inconvenient moment.\nA star of truth, fell from ahigh\nSuch
    lumous ones should wear no lie\nMeteor Knight\nAN ELABORATE TRIDENT\nAppearance
    Ability\n1 Silver rings Can be thrown (d6)\n2 Blackened iron Can be recalled
    to your\nhand when in sight\n3 Two-headed +d8 vs aquatic beings\n4 Faint golden
    glow +d8 vs flying beings\n5 Five prongs Points to fresh water\n6 Telescopic
    shaft Utterly unbreakable\nKNIGHTED BY...\nThe Moonlit Seer\nVIG 5, CLA 16, SPI
    15, 5 GD\n\u2022 A glow of loosely human shape, knows\neverything that moonlight
    has touched.\n\u2022 Only exists under moonlight, strongest\nand most lucid under
    a full moon.\n\u2022 Wants everything to happen at precisely\nthe correct time,
    and nothing significant\nto happen outside of the moon's sight.\nPerson: Ambitious
    parent ~ Name: Reynere ~ Characteristic: Overly familiar\nObject: Shame gem ~
    Beast: Overgrown hawk ~ State: Tearing ~ Theme: Insects\n4\n4\nThe"
